OL,3,CConsumer confidence falls as rapid
OL,4,Cprice rises give households the
OL,5,C'jitters'
OL,7,FConsumer confidence has fallen for the
OL,8,Fthird consecutive month amid household
OL,9,F"jitters" over rapid price rises,
OL,10,Ffigures show.
OL,12,FGfK's long-running consumer confidence
OL,13,Findex fell four points to minus 25 in
OL,14,FApril, following falls of two points
OL,15,Fand three points in March and February
OL,16,Frespectively.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@IO]
