OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777039866
OL,3,CConsumer confidence falls as rapid
OL,4,Cprice rises give households the
OL,5,C'jitters'
OL,7,FThe deepening concern was driven by
OL,8,Fperceptions of the UK economy, with a
OL,9,Fsix-point slide in confidence for the
OL,10,Fnext 12 months to minus 43, its lowest
OL,11,Flevel since February 2023.
OL,13,FConfidence in personal finances over
OL,14,Fthe coming year fell five points to
OL,15,Fminus four ` one point lower than this
OL,16,Ftime last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
