OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777039866
OL,3,CConsumer confidence falls as rapid
OL,4,Cprice rises give households the
OL,5,C'jitters'
OL,7,FThe major purchase index ` an
OL,8,Findicator of confidence in buying big
OL,9,Fticket items ` held steady, albeit at
OL,10,Fminus 18 but one point better than
OL,11,Flast April.
OL,13,FThe only measure to improve was the
OL,14,Fsavings index ` often an indication
OL,15,Fthat households are concerned about
OL,16,Ftheir finances and looking to build
OL,17,Fcontingency funds ` which is up five
OL,18,Fpoints to 32.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
