CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777039866
OL,3,CConsumer confidence falls as rapid
OL,4,Cprice rises give households the
OL,5,C'jitters'
OL,7,FNeil Bellamy, consumer insights
OL,8,Fdirector at GfK, said: "Consumers
OL,9,Freally do have the jitters now.
OL,11,F"It is a year since we last saw a
OL,12,Fmonthly drop of this size, and we have
OL,13,Fto go back to October 2023 to find the
OL,14,Flast time consumer confidence was
OL,15,Flower.
OL,17,F"Everyone is grappling with rapid
OL,18,Fprice rises, especially at the fuel
OL,19,Fpumps, which are taking a dent out of
OL,20,Fhousehold budgets, and people know
OL,21,Ffurther price hikes are coming.
OL,26,@pD@XOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
