OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777039866
OL,3,CConsumer confidence falls as rapid
OL,4,Cprice rises give households the
OL,5,C'jitters'
OL,7,F"Consumer confidence is deteriorating
OL,8,Fsharply, with fuel prices and threats
OL,9,Fof more energy price increases acting
OL,10,Fas constant reminders of inflation.
OL,12,F"While the Gulf crisis is intensifying
OL,13,Fpressures, much of the current strain
OL,14,Freflects earlier domestic cost
OL,15,Fincreases.
OL,17,F"How long can all this disruption and
OL,18,Fpain continue?"
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOUzD@OO]
